    "name": "Antihypertensive Drugs — All Classes (Washout)",
    "description": "All antihypertensive drug ingredient classes: ACE inhibitors (lisinopril, enalapril, ramipril, benazepril, quinapril), ARBs (losartan, valsartan, irbesartan, olmesartan), calcium channel blockers (amlodipine, verapamil), thiazides (hydrochlorothiazide), beta-blockers (metoprolol, atenolol, bisoprolol, carvedilol, labetalol), loop diuretics (furosemide). Used as 365-day washout to ensure new-user design.",
